<tr id="L19"><td><a href="#L19">19</a></td><td>SULU:  No contact, Captain. He blew up all right.</td></tr>

<tr id="L20"><td><a href="#L20">20</a></td><td>KIRK:  Well, we've been anticipating an attack. I'd say what we've just experienced very nearly qualifies.</td></tr>

<tr id="L21"><td><a href="#L21">21</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Yes. It would seem to be an unfriendly act.</td></tr>

