<tr id="L23"><td><a href="#L23">23</a></td><td>KIRK:  Well, there it is. War. We didn't want it, but we've got it.</td></tr>

<tr id="L24"><td><a href="#L24">24</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Curious how often you humans manage to obtain that which you do not want.</td></tr>

