<tr id="L26"><td><a href="#L26">26</a></td><td>SPOCK:  With the outbreak of hostilities, that might not be easy.</td></tr>

<tr id="L27"><td><a href="#L27">27</a></td><td>KIRK:  Lay in a course for Organia, Mister Sulu.</td></tr>

<tr id="L28"><td><a href="#L28">28</a></td><td>SULU:  Aye, aye, sir.</td></tr>

<tr id="L29"><td><a href="#L29">29</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Negotiating with the Organians will be time-consuming, Captain, and time is one thing we'll have the least of.</td></tr>

<tr id="L30"><td><a href="#L30">30</a></td><td>KIRK:  We won't get it by talking about it. The trigger's been pulled. We have to get there before the hammer falls. Ahead warp factor seven.</td></tr>

<tr id="L31"><td><a href="#L31">31</a></td><td>SOMEONE: Captain's log, stardate 3198.4. We have reached Organia and established standard orbit. No signs of hostile activities in this area.</td></tr>

